title: Week 16 NFL DFS Picks & Advice for Saturday and Sunday slates (Fantasy Football 12/24)
description:
Will Brinson and Frank Stampfl link up to offer DFS advice for Week 16 of the NFL season, breaking down both the 3-game Saturday slate and the main Sunday slate. Happy Holidays to all of our listeners!
Saturday slate (2:15)
Bucs-Lions
49ers-Cardinals
Dolphins-Raiders
Sunday slate (19:00)
Falcons-Chiefs
Eagles-Cowboys
Broncos-Chargers
Rams-Seahawks
Browns-Jets
Bears-Jaguars
Bengals-Texans
Giants-Ravens
Panthers-Washington
Colts-Steelers
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
